graph LR
    IR(IR Receiver) -->|ir_in_async| Edge[Edge Detector]
    Edge -->|ir_in_sync| Timer[Pulse Timer]
    Edge -->|edge_rise/fall| Timer
    Timer -->|pulse_data| NEC[NEC Decoder]
    NEC -->|addr/cmd| Format[Output Formatter]
    Format -->|UART Stream| UART[UART TX]
    UART -->|TX| PC(PC Terminal)

    clk((10 MHz)) --> Edge
    clk --> Timer
    clk --> NEC
    clk --> Format
    clk --> UART
